# Keep the build context small and safe. ingest-edge/workers/fake-producer build
# with context = repo root (to reach schema/), so we must exclude the heavy and
# secret bits explicitly.
reference
reference/**
certs
certs/**
.git
**/.git
.env
**/.env
data
**/data
volumes
**/volumes
*.log
**/*.log
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
web/node_modules
ml/artifacts
docs
grafana/dashboards
